ClanBomber2 is a Bomberman like game for Linux

Eight Players can play on one computer or over network.

The following KEYS are valid:

Keymap 1
--------
move left:	Cursor Left
move right:	Cursor Right
move up:	Cursor Up
move down:	Cursor Down
place bomb:	Enter

Keymap 2
--------
move left:	a
move right:	d
move up:	w
move down:	s
place bomb:	Tab

Keymap 3
--------
move left:	j
move right:	l
move up:	i
move down:	k
place bomb:	Space


If more than three players want to play, the others have to use 
joypads/joysticks.


display fps:		F1
quit current game: 	Esc
pause			P

debug keys (ONLY IF DEBUG SUPPORT IS COMPILED IN)
-------------------------------------------------------
add AI_DOK player during game:	F2
add AI_MASS during game:	F3
change level during game:	/ and * on numeric pad


Please test it and write us with your opinion

http://www.clanbomber.de
